<section id="meta_id">
  <title>id</title>

  <para>Identifier - a character string used to identify a <olink
      targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metadata.xml" targetptr="metadata"
        ><code>&lt;metadata></code></olink> or <olink
      targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metagroup.xml" targetptr="metagroup"
        ><code>&lt;metaGroup></code></olink> element.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> NMTOKEN</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis><olink
    targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metadata.xml" targetptr="metadata"
    ><code>&lt;metadata></code></olink> and <olink
      targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metagroup.xml" targetptr="metagroup"
      ><code>&lt;metaGroup></code></olink></para>
<itemizedlist>
  <title>Constraints</title>
  <listitem>
    <para>The values of <link linkend="meta_id"><code>id</code></link> attributes <glossterm>must</glossterm> be unique among all <olink
      targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metagroup.xml" targetptr="metagroup"
      ><code>&lt;metaGroup></code></olink> 
      and <olink
        targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metadata.xml" targetptr="metadata"
        ><code>&lt;metadata></code></olink> elements within the given enclosing 
      <olink
        targetdoc="../elements/metadata/metadata.xml" targetptr="metadata"
        ><code>&lt;metadata></code></olink> element.
    </para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>  


</section>
